{"word":"Hamath","slug":"hamath","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hamath</b> <a href=\"#/H2574\">H2574</a> <br/> Called also Hemath.<br/> A city of upper Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=21'>Num 13:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=8'>Num 34:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=5'>Jos 13:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=65'>1Ki 8:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=16'>Eze 47:16</a><br/> Inhabited by Canaanites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=18'>Gen 10:18</a><br/> Prosperity of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=2'>Amo 6:2</a><br/> David receives gifts of gold and silver from Toi, king of Hamath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=10'>2Sa 8:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=3'>1Ch 18:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=10'>1Ch 18:10</a><br/> Conquest of, by Jeroboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=25'>2Ki 14:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=28'>2Ki 14:28</a><br/> Conquest of, by the Chaldeans<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=21'>2Ki 25:21</a><br/> Israelites taken captive to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=11&verse=11'>Isa 11:11</a><br/> Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=23'>Jer 49:23</a><br/> Solomon builds store cities in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=4'>2Ch 8:4</a>"}]}